<paragraph blockId="10.[192,1440,770,890]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">
The genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomson" authorityYear="1868" box="[380,518,770,794]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Psyllotoxus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[380,518,770,794]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">Psyllotoxus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
currently contains two described species, 
<taxonomicName authority="Thomson, 1868" authorityName="Thomson" authorityYear="1868" box="[1050,1439,770,794]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Psyllotoxus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="griseocinctus">
<emphasis box="[1050,1237,771,794]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">P. griseocinctus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Thomson, J." box="[1247,1439,770,794]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" pagination="41 - 92" refId="ref12243" refString="Thomson, J. 1868. Revision du groupe des onciderites (Lamites, cerambycides, coleopteres). Physis Recueil d'Histoire Naturelle 2 (5): 41 - 92." type="journal article" year="1868">Thomson, 1868</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation box="[201,316,802,826]" captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="15.[192,275,1619,1641]" captionText="Figure 6. Two species of Psyllotoxus Thomson, 1868. a) P. griseocinctus Thomson, 1868, male, dorsal habitus. b) P. inexpectatus Martins and Galileo, 1990, holotype male, dorsal habitus. c) P. griseocinctus Thomson, 1868, male, close-up of pronotum and elytral humeri. d) P. inexpectatus Martins and Galileo, 1990, holotype male, close-up of pronotum and elytral humeri." pageId="10" pageNumber="9">Fig. 6a, d</figureCitation>
) and 
<taxonomicName authority="Martins and Galileo, 1990" authorityName="Martins and Galileo" authorityYear="1990" box="[385,889,802,826]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Psyllotoxus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inexpectatus">
<emphasis box="[385,561,803,826]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">P. inexpectatus</emphasis>
Martins and 
<bibRefCitation author="Galileo, M. H. M. &amp; U. R. Martins" box="[727,889,802,826]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" pagination="11 - 15" refId="ref11565" refString="Galileo, M. H. M., and U. R. Martins. 1990. Longicornios do museu Paraense Emilio Goeldi I. Novas especies em Sphaerionini e Onciderini (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae). Boletim do Museo Paraense Emilio Goeldi, serie Zoologia 6 (1): 11 - 15." type="journal article" year="1990">Galileo, 1990</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation box="[905,1024,802,826]" captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="15.[192,275,1619,1641]" captionText="Figure 6. Two species of Psyllotoxus Thomson, 1868. a) P. griseocinctus Thomson, 1868, male, dorsal habitus. b) P. inexpectatus Martins and Galileo, 1990, holotype male, dorsal habitus. c) P. griseocinctus Thomson, 1868, male, close-up of pronotum and elytral humeri. d) P. inexpectatus Martins and Galileo, 1990, holotype male, close-up of pronotum and elytral humeri." pageId="10" pageNumber="9">Fig. 6b, d</figureCitation>
). A third species was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Giacomel, F." box="[192,388,834,858]" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" pagination="1 - 5" refId="ref11621" refString="Giacomel, F. 1991. Nove especie de Psylotoxus Thomson, 1868 do Mato Grosso, Brasil (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae). Acta Biolo'gica Paranaense 20 (1 - 4): 1 - 5." type="journal article" year="1991">Giacomel (1991)</bibRefCitation>
and later synonymized with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Martins and Galileo" authorityYear="1990" box="[729,899,835,858]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Psyllotoxus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inexpectatus">
<emphasis box="[729,899,835,858]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">P. inexpectatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The following key treats all currently known species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomson" authorityYear="1868" box="[312,450,866,890]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Psyllotoxus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[312,450,866,890]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="9">Psyllotoxus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
including two new species described herein.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
